title: How to Prioritize Your Day | Tom Bilyeu AMA
description: Tom Bilyeu answers questions asked by the community. You can submit your questions in advance to ama@impacttheory.com, with the subject line “AMA Question”.   Sponsors: Fundrise: Get your first 3 months of fees waived by going to fundrise.com/impact Skillshare: Start learning on Skillshare today at skillshare.com/ImpactTheory Blinkist: Visit www.blinkist.com/IMPACT to try out the premium service completely free for 7 days!   PEOPLE MENTIONED: John Doerr [4:04] Daniel Amen [8:02] Jim Kwik https://bit.ly/2Cs6WjQ [13:02] Peter Attia https://bit.ly/2Rhmtvm [29:44] Dom D’agostino https://bit.ly/2Se2MBz [29:45] Ken Berry https://bit.ly/2EKPWb7  [33:58] Ben Greenfield [35:30] Dr. Rhonda Patrick [35:40]   BOOKS MENTIONED: Measure What Matters by John Doerr https://amzn.to/2RhtLyS [4:04]   QUESTIONS: How Tom schedules his day with an important things list, and OKRs [3:04] Why you’re struggling to work hard and smart at the same time and how to deal with negative thoughts [5:32] How to train your memory and be kinder to yourself when you make mistakes [12:08] How to deal with depression and grieving (it’s in these moments you will show yourself who you’re becoming) [21:34] The biggest changes to Tom’s eating habits over the years and why he likes Keto [25:09] When to exercise so your muscles uptake the most glycogen [33:58]
